1949;;Red Canyon;;American;;George Sherman;;Ann Blyth, Howard Duff, George Brent;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red_Canyon_(1949_film);;The plot revolves around Black Velvet, a wild stallion that runs rampant across the range. Two people, reformed bad man Lin Sloan (played by Howard Duff) and tomboyish farmer's daughter Lucy Bostel (Ann Blyth), think they can tame him. In the process, they tame each other.